These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, time-travel, mystery, action, adventure, zombie
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, funk, dubstep, electronic, disco, d&b, salsa
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, baseball, sailing, cycling, basketball, skateboarding
 1. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the fan of funk and the fan of country##2
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 6. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the fan of electronic is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person watching action movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of dubstep##1
11. the fan of d&b is the person watching mystery movies##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
13. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of disco##1
14. the person watching adventure movies is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | sports     | adventure | martial-arts | mystery | zombie  | time-travel  |
| Music-Genre   | country  | electronic        | funk  | salsa     | d&b   | dubstep       | disco   |
| Sport         | rowing   | skateboarding | sailing    | baseball  | cycling | basketball | snowboarding |

