.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, dutch, malaysian, german, chinese, italian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, surfing, cycling, rowing, climbing, water-polo
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, tram, quad-bike, subway, motorbike, airplane
 1. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is the italian##1
 6. the nigerian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the nigerian is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person driving the airplane##2
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the german##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is the argentine##1
13. the malaysian is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the argentine is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | chinese | italian      | malaysian     | nigerian  | german | dutch | argentine |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | baseball | climbing | surfing | water-polo | cycling   | rowing  |
| Transport     | tram   | motorbike     | airplane        | quad-bike  | subway   | snowmobile       | jet-ski      |

