10. the security-guard is on the right of the mechanic##1
11. the person driving the train is the doctor##1
12. the security-guard is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the architect##1
14. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
