The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, jazz, ambient, folk, electronic, techno, r&b
7 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, rat, lizard, horse, dog, rabbit
 1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the owner of the dog is between the fan of electronic and the fan of ambient##2
 3. the fan of rock is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 5. the fan of rock is the firefighter##1
 6. the lawyer is in the middle##1
 7. the accountant is the fan of techno##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the fan of rock is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the software-developer is the owner of the horse##1
11. the firefighter is on the right of the mechanic##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the left of the dressmaker##1
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
14. the fan of jazz is on the left of the firefighter##1
15. the software-developer is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
